to my body temporarily.

475
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:48,100
San,

476
00:26:48,560 --> 00:26:50,380
I know what you're trying to do.

477
00:26:50,470 --> 00:26:52,860
I won't miss out
on such an important moment.

478
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,810
Father,

479
00:27:04,710 --> 00:27:06,250
I want to get engaged to Wu.

480
00:27:06,510 --> 00:27:07,770
I hope you

481
00:27:07,880 --> 00:27:09,180
and Mother

482
00:27:09,470 --> 00:27:11,050
can be our witnesses.

483
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:16,660
Wu,

484
00:27:17,030 --> 00:27:18,730
I'll be honest with you.

485
00:27:19,510 --> 00:27:21,330
To us,

486
00:27:21,470 --> 00:27:23,460
you were already
a part of our family long ago.

487
00:27:26,920 --> 00:27:29,660
I lost my mother when I was very young.

488
00:27:29,990 --> 00:27:32,250
I barged into
the human world by accident.

489
00:27:32,800 --> 00:27:35,860
Luckily, I got to know
San when I was young.

490
00:27:36,320 --> 00:27:38,050
We supported each other
throughout our journey.

491
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:39,940
We've been through
many hardships together.

492
00:27:40,190 --> 00:27:42,460
San and I were already one long ago.

493
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:44,050
Our hearts were in sync.

494
00:27:46,230 --> 00:27:47,860
To me,

495
00:27:48,190 --> 00:27:50,420
you were a part of my family
long ago as well.

496
00:27:51,710 --> 00:27:53,330
I'm very happy

497
00:27:53,670 --> 00:27:55,420
that you can accept me.

498
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:57,839
Yin,

499
00:27:57,840 --> 00:27:59,010
did you hear that?

500
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:10,250
Once, I blamed the heavens
for being unfair to me.

501
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,319
But ever since I met San,

502
00:28:13,320 --> 00:28:14,570
I knew

503
00:28:15,840 --> 00:28:17,220
that I would become

504
00:28:17,800 --> 00:28:20,420
the luckiest person in the world.

505
00:28:21,120 --> 00:28:22,050
No.

506
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:25,460
I'm the luckiest person in the world.

507
00:28:27,320 --> 00:28:31,220
What have I done to deserve
a great wife like you?

508
00:28:34,670 --> 00:28:36,380
I will notify my parents,

509
00:28:37,510 --> 00:28:39,010
the gods and deities,

510
00:28:40,840 --> 00:28:42,330
and all living beings

511
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:47,420
that you're my wife.

512
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:52,660
♪Thoughts of you flow like raging tides♪

513
00:28:53,360 --> 00:28:58,220
♪The past becomes blurry
amidst the wind and tears♪

514
00:29:03,080 --> 00:29:03,799
Look!

515
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:04,730
A shooting star!

516
00:29:05,470 --> 00:29:06,250
Look.

517
00:29:11,080 --> 00:29:12,940
The night sky looks gorgeous.

518
00:29:13,710 --> 00:29:15,079
I'm sure this shooting star

519
00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:17,140
has granted the wish of many people.

520
00:29:18,280 --> 00:29:22,900
♪The secret tangled on one's wrist♪

521
00:29:23,240 --> 00:29:28,340
♪Because of you, I was able to♪

522
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:32,580
♪Sense the world♪

523
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:50,260
♪Longing transcends
the distance of time and space♪

524
00:29:50,720 --> 00:29:57,700
♪In dreams, I embrace the faraway you♪

525
00:29:58,120 --> 00:30:03,020
♪Parting, alone, through trials♪

526
00:30:03,600 --> 00:30:09,380
♪Just to defy destiny with you♪

527
00:30:09,800 --> 00:30:12,740
♪The starry river of the night♪

528
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:17,460
♪Sketches the view we saw together♪

529
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:19,220
♪Honors the hardships♪

530
00:30:19,400 --> 00:30:24,740
♪Endured along the thorny path♪

531
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:29,780
♪The glow of the soul ring
shall never fade♪

532
00:30:30,280 --> 00:30:34,860
♪With unwavering faith♪

533
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:40,020
♪I write the next miracle♪

534
00:30:40,880 --> 00:30:41,860
Alright now.

535
00:30:42,430 --> 00:30:43,970
I know you're happy.

536
00:30:49,320 --> 00:30:50,330
San,

537
00:30:50,800 --> 00:30:51,799
Wu,

538
00:30:51,800 --> 00:30:54,940
since you two have gotten engaged today,

539
00:30:56,600 --> 00:30:58,010
your mother and I hope

540
00:30:58,750 --> 00:31:00,399
that you two

541
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,180
can be with each other

542
00:31:03,230 --> 00:31:04,530
through thick and thin.

543
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:09,380
♪That I do not fear the change of time♪

544
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:16,980
♪Because of you,
I'm sure of what to say.♪

545
00:31:18,670 --> 00:31:19,940
Dear parents,

