601
00:34:47,990 --> 00:34:48,949
Stop dilly-dallying, then.

602
00:34:48,950 --> 00:34:50,140
Pack your belongings.

603
00:34:51,880 --> 00:34:53,020
That's right, San.

604
00:34:53,030 --> 00:34:53,540
Let's go!

605
