in Xingdou Forest.

624
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,279
We never

625
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,029
forgot about that.

626
00:36:09,030 --> 00:36:10,839
We were planning to hold
an engagement ceremony for you two

627
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:12,949
before we depart for Haishen Island.

628
00:36:12,950 --> 00:36:14,450
It was meant to be a surprise.

629
00:36:14,470 --> 00:36:17,109
But you guys actually ditched us

630
00:36:17,110 --> 00:36:18,719
and held the ceremony without us.

631
00:36:18,720 --> 00:36:19,469
That's too much.

632
00:36:19,470 --> 00:36:20,359
That's right.

633
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:22,359
You abducted Wu behind my back.

634
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:24,109
You have no regard
for her family members at all,

635
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,450
