640
00:36:39,840 --> 00:36:40,930
That's right.

641
00:36:41,150 --> 00:36:42,839
Wu doesn't know how the world works.

642
00:36:42,840 --> 00:36:44,629
She was duped by San.

643
00:36:44,630 --> 00:36:46,149
We have to uphold justice for her,

644
00:36:46,150 --> 00:36:46,810
