645
00:36:47,280 --> 00:36:48,239
That's right.

646
00:36:48,240 --> 00:36:49,719
If he wants to marry Wu,

647
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:51,060
he has to prepare betrothal gifts

648
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,549
and proceed with all the rites
and ceremonies.

649
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:53,250
Wu,

650
00:36:53,360 --> 00:36:55,100
