if any of the processes are lacking.

651
00:36:56,240 --> 00:36:57,980
(They have a point.)

652
00:36:58,320 --> 00:37:00,580
(The engagement was too hasty.)

653
00:37:00,990 --> 00:37:03,060
(It felt like I was duped.)

654
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:06,149
Wu,

655
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:07,810
