656
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,020
Hey, you guys.

657
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:11,509
You guys can choose to be envious

658
00:37:11,510 --> 00:37:12,890
or even jealous.

659
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:15,290
But don't cancel my engagement.

660
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:17,580
Fight me if you're upset with it.

661
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:18,919
Fight you, huh?

662
00:37:18,920 --> 00:37:19,759
Ao,

663
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:20,700
drag him out.

664
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,949
How dare you dupe Wu?

665
00:37:21,950 --> 00:37:23,029
We'll beat you up.

666
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:23,509
Let's go!

667
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:24,580
Drag him out!

668
00:37:24,990 --> 00:37:25,930
Come on!

669
00:37:26,070 --> 00:37:26,759
Hurry!

670
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:27,540
Come with us!

671
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:29,410
You're beating me for real?

672
00:37:31,680 --> 00:37:34,060
When can I receive such a treatment?

673
00:37:35,950 --> 00:37:36,629
Sir.

674
00:37:36,630 --> 00:37:37,660
Sir.

675
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,020
Sir.

676
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:47,509
San,

677
00:37:47,510 --> 00:37:48,450
Wu,

678
00:37:48,720 --> 00:37:49,980
congratulations.

679
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:54,370
Thank you, Sir.

680
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:55,660
By the way,

681
00:37:55,720 --> 00:37:56,839
you came back at the right time.

682
00:37:56,840 --> 00:37:58,660
His Majesty is inviting you
to the palace.

683
00:38:00,070 --> 00:38:01,060
Sect Leader Tang,

684
00:38:01,550 --> 00:38:03,319
I heard that you're going on a trip

685
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,370
to boost your power.

686
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:08,700
How long will the trip take?

687
00:38:08,950 --> 00:38:11,239
At least 3 years, and at most 50 years.

688
00:38:11,240 --> 00:38:12,620
So, once we part ways,

689
00:38:12,950 --> 00:38:15,810
we might not be able
to see each other again.

690
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,330
Xue Beng.

691
00:38:36,150 --> 00:38:37,290
Sect Leader Tang,

692
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,620
this is what he's supposed to do.

693
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:41,700
Your Highness,

694
00:38:42,150 --> 00:38:43,149
what are you doing?

695
00:38:43,150 --> 00:38:45,100
Sect Leader Tang, please accept my bow.

696
00:38:45,470 --> 00:38:47,660
You saved my father from danger.

697
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:50,279
