on Father's behalf and for myself.

699
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,410
Your Highness, please get up.

700
00:38:59,680 --> 00:39:00,879
I don't deserve this.

701
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:04,060
I hope that you can take
Xue Beng as your student.

702
00:39:04,150 --> 00:39:06,580
I hope that you can look after him.

703
00:39:07,240 --> 00:39:09,719
Therefore, it's reasonable
for him to bow to you.

704
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:12,810
You deserve the bow.

705
00:39:15,240 --> 00:39:15,890
Your Majesty,

706
00:39:16,430 --> 00:39:17,949
I do not deserve

707
00:39:17,950 --> 00:39:19,679
to be His Highness's teacher.

708
00:39:19,680 --> 00:39:20,770
I trust you.

709
00:39:21,110 --> 00:39:22,410
You deserve it.

710
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:25,930
Xue Beng

711
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,660
