712
00:39:28,470 --> 00:39:29,770
However, he's actually
enduring in silence.

713
00:39:34,550 --> 00:39:38,060
I'm willing to hand Tiandou to him.

714
00:39:38,510 --> 00:39:40,220
However, he isn't fully fledged yet.

715
00:39:40,430 --> 00:39:41,810
I'm worried about him.

716
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:43,949
He needs someone

717
00:39:43,950 --> 00:39:45,980
who can support him

718
00:39:46,030 --> 00:39:47,700
and who he can trust.

719
00:39:48,720 --> 00:39:50,180
He trusts you.

720
00:39:50,630 --> 00:39:52,060
He admires you as well.

721
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:56,700
You're the best teacher he can have.

722
00:39:58,950 --> 00:40:00,250
Sir,

723
00:40:00,680 --> 00:40:02,020
