724
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,450
According to our title,

725
00:40:19,920 --> 00:40:21,370
I'm your teacher.

726
00:40:22,150 --> 00:40:23,700
However, according to our identities,

727
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:26,220
I'll always be your subject.

728
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:36,890
Tang San, sect leader of Tang Clan,
receive the imperial decree.

729
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:39,810
This is a special decree.

730
00:40:39,950 --> 00:40:44,250
