He shall be appointed as the crown prince's Grand Preceptor.

731
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,429
He does not need to bow to the ruler.

732
00:40:46,430 --> 00:40:48,220
He shall be a prince
with a different surname,

733
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:50,770
with his title being Lan Hao.

734
00:40:51,760 --> 00:40:54,100
Thank you, Your Majesty.

735
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,100
Prince Lan Hao,

736
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:59,660
