the symbol of your identity.

737
00:40:59,990 --> 00:41:03,290
This is
the Vast Sea and Universe Shield.

738
00:41:03,510 --> 00:41:05,060
In a sense,

739
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:08,250
it can be considered a soul tool.

740
00:41:08,920 --> 00:41:11,620
This item serves as the symbol
of Prince Lan Hao.

741
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:14,290
It has plenty of functions.

742
00:41:14,510 --> 00:41:16,220
Prince Lan Hao,
just inject your soul power

743
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:18,700
into it when you head back.

744
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:20,330
You'll understand it after that.

745
00:41:31,680 --> 00:41:34,250
It should be of use to you

746
00:41:34,630 --> 00:41:36,450
during your training.

747
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:48,879
Your Highness, I shall

748
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:51,450
do my best to assist you
as long as I'm around.

749
00:41:51,760 --> 00:41:54,620
I shall assist you in creating
a prosperous Tiandou.

750
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,810
How did this happen?

751
00:42:35,030 --> 00:42:36,890
It feels like a mysterious power
has flowed into this realm

752
00:42:37,200 --> 00:42:39,620
after the appearance
of the Vast Sea and Universe Shield.

753
00:42:43,320 --> 00:42:45,580
I even feel a little giddy.

754
00:43:26,470 --> 00:43:27,850
(How many years has it been?)

755
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:28,989
(Now, I've finally found someone)

756
00:43:28,990 --> 00:43:31,180
(who can withstand
the power of the vast ocean.)

757
00:43:31,360 --> 00:43:32,890
(But the result will depend on)

758
00:43:33,280 --> 00:43:36,220
(whether or not
you can withstand the upcoming trials.)

759
00:44:10,560 --> 00:44:17,460
♪Longing is an unknown riddle♪

760
00:44:17,520 --> 00:44:24,799
♪Mistaking the wrong person in the crowd♪

761
00:44:24,800 --> 00:44:30,119
♪Thoughts of you flow like raging tides♪

762
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:36,500
♪The past becomes blurry
amidst the wind and tears♪

763
00:44:46,150 --> 00:44:53,420
