the distance of time and space♪

764
00:44:53,680 --> 00:45:00,919
♪In dreams, I embrace the faraway you♪

765
00:45:00,920 --> 00:45:06,479
♪Parting, alone, through trials♪

766
00:45:06,480 --> 00:45:12,740
♪Just to defy destiny with you♪

767
00:45:12,800 --> 00:45:20,700
♪The starry river of the night
sketches the view we saw together♪

768
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:28,580
♪Honors the hardships
endured along the thorny path♪

769
00:45:28,680 --> 00:45:33,260
♪The glow of the soul ring
shall never fade♪

770
00:45:33,280 --> 00:45:40,580
♪With unwavering faith,
I write the next miracle♪

771
00:45:52,760 --> 00:46:00,380
♪The unfinished story must be tested by
hardships before it can continue♪

772
00:46:01,160 --> 00:46:04,140
♪Because of you, the answer is clear♪

773
00:46:04,240 --> 00:46:08,599
♪Through mountains and seas,
I've promised to come back♪

774
00:46:08,600 --> 00:46:13,140
♪That I do not fear the change of time♪

775
00:46:13,440 --> 00:46:26,940
♪Because of you,
I'm sure of what to say. I do♪

